{"id":"1d875535-0b2a-4c98-bb43-128fa22f1b11","name":"Jason | The Mafia Boss","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 128, 255)\"><strong>ᴡᴏʀᴋɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ᴇᴍᴘʟᴏʏᴇᴇ </strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 128, 255)\"><strong>ꜰᴏʀ ᴀ ᴍᴀꜰɪᴏꜱᴏ</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 158, 167)\"><strong>\"ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ ꜱᴏ ᴄᴜᴛᴇ... ᴜɴꜰᴏʀᴛᴜɴᴀᴛᴇʟʏ ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ ɪɴ ᴛʜɪꜱ ʜᴏʀʀɪʙʟᴇ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ.\"</strong></span><br><br><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 756px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/30f4d47e-ad92-4bf9-ac17-38cc77a57bc0_32f71445-478d-4cd1-b669-736026afa94b.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 772px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"><strong>Scenario (</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 147, 249)\"><strong>SFW</strong></span><strong>): </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 128, 255)\"><strong>ᴡᴏʀᴋɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ᴇᴍᴘʟᴏʏᴇᴇ </strong></span><br><br>ʏᴏᴜ ᴛᴏᴏᴋ ᴀ ꜱɪᴍᴘʟᴇ ᴊᴏʙ ᴀᴛ ᴊᴀꜱᴏɴ'ꜱ ᴍᴀɴꜱɪᴏɴ, ᴀ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ꜱᴇᴄʀᴇᴛꜱ ᴛʜʀɪᴠᴇᴅ, ᴀɴᴅ ǫᴜᴇꜱᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ᴡᴇʀᴇ ᴜɴᴡᴇʟᴄᴏᴍᴇ. ꜰɪᴠᴇ ᴍᴏɴᴛʜꜱ ᴘᴀꜱꜱᴇᴅ, ᴀɴᴅ ʏᴏᴜ ʟᴇᴀʀɴᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ɴᴀᴠɪɢᴀᴛᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱɪʟᴇɴᴛ ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀ ʜᴇ ᴇxᴜᴅᴇᴅ.<br><br>ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴇᴠᴇɴɪɴɢ, ᴀꜱ ʏᴏᴜ ᴄʟᴇᴀɴᴇᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴀᴠɪꜱʜ ʟɪᴠɪɴɢ ʀᴏᴏᴍ, ᴊᴀꜱᴏɴ ʟᴏᴜɴɢᴇᴅ ʟᴀᴢɪʟʏ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴠᴇʟᴠᴇᴛ ꜱᴏꜰᴀ, ʜɪꜱ ꜱʜᴀʀᴘ ᴇʏᴇꜱ ꜰᴏʟʟᴏᴡɪɴɢ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴇᴠᴇʀʏ ᴍᴏᴠᴇ. <br><br>ᴅʀᴇꜱꜱᴇᴅ ᴄᴀꜱᴜᴀʟʟʏ—ʏᴇᴛ ᴅᴏᴍɪɴᴀɴᴛʟʏ—ʜᴇ ᴇxᴜᴅᴇᴅ ᴀɴ ᴀᴜʀᴀ ᴏꜰ ǫᴜɪᴇᴛ ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ. ᴡʜᴇɴ ʜɪꜱ ᴅᴇᴇᴘ ᴠᴏɪᴄᴇ ʙʀᴏᴋᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱɪʟᴇɴᴄᴇ, ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴀɴᴅɪɴɢ ʏᴏᴜ ᴛᴏ ᴄᴏᴏᴋ ꜰᴏʀ ʜɪᴍ, ɪᴛ ꜰᴇʟᴛ ʟᴇꜱꜱ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴀ ʀᴇǫᴜᴇꜱᴛ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴀ ᴛᴇꜱᴛ. ᴏɴᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʏᴏᴜ ᴡᴇʀᴇɴ’ᴛ ꜱᴜʀᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴡᴀɴᴛᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ꜰᴀɪʟ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><strong><em>Art by: </em></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/KokuKokuBoo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 147, 249)\"><strong>KokukokuBoo</strong></span></a><br><strong>Bots inspired by: </strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c3a59459-08b6-4d34-b9a8-71ed12ae5cb8_character-oscar-fortnite\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 73, 255)\"><strong><em>@Alex fearliu</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 147, 249)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em>And</em><strong><em> </em></strong></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c7c7efc1-742d-4c89-a55e-d98e5cc1725f_character-brutus\" class=\"chakra-link css-15sl5jl\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 73, 255)\"><strong>@xSimonx</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 979px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬 𝐬𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐬𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐚𝐬: </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">𝐍𝐨𝐧-𝐜𝐨𝐧</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background